OL,6,FHelen Steel reports
OL,8,Fsays he's 'given in' and switched the
OL,9,Fchimes off - opting for a hand held
OL,10,Fbell instead.
OL,12,FJohn Barton, owner of Harrison's Ices
OL,13,Fin Grimsby, said 'it just gives him
OL,14,Fless of a headache' because bells -
OL,15,Funlike chimes - are not regulated by
