OL,3,CIce cream seller ditches chimes for
OL,4,Cbells after noise complaints
OL,6,FAs well as guidance over the frequency
OL,7,Fand volume, there are laws governing
OL,8,Fice cream van chimes, including that
OL,9,Fthey can must be operated between the
OL,10,Fhours of noon and 7pm, and "as not to
OL,11,Fgive reasonable cause for annoyance to
OL,12,Fpersons in the vicinity."
OL,14,FJohn's favourite song to play is 'Just
OL,15,Fone Cornetto' - and up until now;
OL,16,Fthey'd had just one complaint. But -
OL,17,Fsince they took their complaints to
OL,18,Fthe news - some more residents have
OL,19,Fcomplained to them.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
