OL,3,CIce cream seller ditches chimes for
OL,4,Cbells after noise complaints
OL,6,FJohn said: "I've got a bell because
OL,7,Fthere are no regulations on a bell,
OL,8,Fthey aren't like chimes, where they
OL,9,Fare regulated because they are
OL,10,Felectronic.
OL,12,F"It's a loop hole, it's to avoid the
OL,13,Felectronic chimes, but we don't want
OL,14,Fto be out later than 7:30pm anyway,
OL,15,Fbut it's just than half an hour to
OL,16,Fsave ourselves a headache."
