OL,3,CIce cream seller ditches chimes for
OL,4,Cbells after noise complaints
OL,6,FJamie Tomlinson who sells ice creams
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've got families to feed, the
OL,8,Findustry is different to what it used
OL,9,Fto be, leave us alone, let us get on
OL,10,Fwith it."
OL,12,FEast Lindsey District Council says it
OL,13,Fhas only so far received one complaint
OL,14,F- but if it received another, it
OL,15,Fpreviously said it would have to take
OL,16,Fsome action.
